{"tid":2172917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美駐歐轟炸機　罕有全「核配置」震懾俄國","createTime":"2020-08-25T02:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T03:23:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0f6e02c816c3309857ce796fb587822d7d40a2","tid":2172917,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200825/photo/bkn-20200825100051356-0825_00912_001_01p.jpg?20200825100407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200825%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200825100051356-0825_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20200825100407&h=0d482dad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n挪威軍方公開F16戰機與美軍B52H轟炸機演練的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為應對俄羅斯的威脅，美國上周六（22日）在英國部署6架B52H戰略轟炸機；挪威軍方周一（24日）公開該國戰機與美軍轟炸機演練的畫面。與此同時，軍事專家發現，今次這批部署海外的美軍轟炸機，罕有全數具備投射核武的能力。<br />\n<br />\n挪威軍方沒有透露這次演習何時展開，由於美軍轟炸機從本土出發後，罕有取道格陵蘭北部及挪威海上空前往英國，因此可能順便與挪威F16戰機演練。挪威軍方表示，美國在區內部署轟炸機有助加強北約成員國之間的合作性，而演習測試挪威協調行動的能力，又預告F35A隱形戰機也將與美軍轟炸機聯合行動。<br />\n<br />\nB52H是美軍一款可以發射核武的戰略轟炸機，近年不時在歐洲及印太地區執行轟炸機特遣隊任務並短暫部署。軍事專家指今次派駐英國的B52H，全數具備投射核武的能力，與過往部署時部分轟炸機只能搭載常規彈藥的混合編隊不同。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，俄羅斯國防部周一表示，當天在波羅的海國際水域上空，發現3個目標飛近俄國邊界，於是派出一架蘇27戰機攔截，並識別它們分別是美國RC135偵察機、德國P3C海上巡邏機及瑞典灣流偵察機；其中德國軍機在500米高度以時速250公里飛行，企圖避開俄軍的探測，而涉事3架軍機其後飛離俄國邊界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200825/photo/bkn-20200825100051356-0825_00912_001_02p.jpg?20200825100407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200825%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200825100051356-0825_00912_001_02p.jpg%3F20200825100407&h=55568485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n挪威F16戰機（前）與美軍B52H轟炸機（後）聯合行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200825/photo/bkn-20200825100051356-0825_00912_001_03p.jpg?20200825100407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200825%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200825100051356-0825_00912_001_03p.jpg%3F20200825100407&h=d473e1a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n挪威F16戰機（下）與美軍B52H轟炸機（上）組成飛行編隊。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200825/bkn-20200825100051356-0825_00912_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c8ffd72af17ce064054c3603ac50b3b10b4007f6","tid":2172917,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:14:55.000Z","msg":"其中德國軍機在500米高度以時速250公里飛行，企圖避開俄軍的探測<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0536c9ef486dd669b10bb355fe79b8fa7fdcea79","tid":2172917,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc829f46607c173a50ff2c133f53a1c8b1f6f09a","tid":2172917,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:21:00.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2d7690380a7f865a3bee1fc542ccd075ac9239","tid":2172917,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3be1a07f147cc6be4e4220e3b0f01cefbd2ee8","tid":2172917,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"想deploy warhead有咩理由唔用導彈而用bomber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}